      %li The date to the right of the "Upcoming" title is today's date.
      %li Customize your list colors by hovering over the list title and clicking on the color icon that appears to the right. Click a swatch or input a Hex value.
      %li Delete a list by clicking the X icon to the right of the list title.
      %li Delete a task by editing the task, deleting all of it's text, and pressing ENTER.
      %li View the entire history of a list by clicking the "View all" link at the bottom of the list.
